text: First time patronising this food court run by food paradise inside safra mount Faber.  The china lady of SWK noodle was friendly.  Even though once again, I ran into issues with Safra discount and e voucher but she maintained friendly.  I ordered pig trotter rice and lady asked me to get the set including dumplings at 8 SGD as at 10 Aug 2024 Overall I enjoyed the meal.

Please dont even try the sarawak laksa here.

Totally taste different than original sarawak laksa. You can only taste disappointment here. Youre welcome
Telok Blangah SAFRA. Ordered pork trotter rice. Quite good. Tasty, fragrant tender pork. Most on the queue ordered tis and braised pork rice.
I like the kolo mee , better than the other shops in SG that I have previously dined at. Agreed with the  review on the poor quality of the char siew though.
Decent food. Friendly staff and pretty nice atmosphere to sit in.
